# Copy to ".env" in THIS folder (repo root), then restart: npx expo start --clear
#
# Physical phone + API on same PC: use your Wi‑Fi IPv4 (see ipconfig / ifconfig).
# Android emulator: http://10.0.2.2:3000
# iOS Simulator (Mac): http://localhost:3000
#
# No trailing slash. Leave empty to run app offline (no backend sync).
EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://192.168.1.100:3000
#
# EAS installable builds (testing / preview profile): set EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL in expo.dev
# → Environment variables → Preview. See docs/TESTING_WITH_BACKEND.md section 6.
